udata	segment

						; Display scheme for use
						; by Generic objects, gadgets,
						; applications, & the specific
						; UI.  Ends up being passed
						; around in GStates, though
						; specific UI elements can
						; look directly at the
						; variables stored here in
						; dgroup.
